<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <title>Privacy Policy - Square Chatroom</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-start">
  <header class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-6 shadow-md">
    <h1 class="text-3xl text-center font-bold">Square Chatroom</h1>
  </header>

  <main class="w-full max-w-3xl p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md mt-8 mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h2>

    <p class="mb-3">
      Square Chatroom respects your privacy. We only collect your Google profile information (name and email) to identify you and notify the admin for chat access.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-3">
      Your data is <strong>never shared with third parties</strong> and is only used to manage chatroom access.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-3">
      You can contact the admin at <a href="mailto:<%= process.env.ADMIN_NOTIFY_EMAIL %>" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">admin email</a> for any privacy concerns.
    </p>
    <p>
      By using this app, you consent to the collection and use of your Google profile information as described above.
    </p>
  </main>

  <footer class="w-full bg-gray-200 text-center py-4 mt-auto">
    <p class="text-gray-700">&copy; 2025 Square Chatroom. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
